---
title: Gnocchi in Pork Ragu with Spinach and Parmesan
description: We're bringing in gnocchi tonight to switch up the typical spaghetti and meat sauce dinner. Hearty gnocchi lends satisfying texture to every bite, while we keep it classic by finishing it off with Parmesan cheese!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gnocchis-a-la-sauce-ragu-au-porc-52c87009.jpg
